CHANGELOG

This file records the main changes of the releases.

0.0.3
  * more platform independet by detecting what os is running.
  * renamed vimplguin to ui
  * set up a update-site at http://vimplugin.sf.net/update

0.0.2
  * reference to vim binary went to a preference page
  * a HACKING file t oattract developers
  * an ant buildfile as a stub to automate the build of packages

0.0.1
  * first public release
  * hard coded reference to "vim" binary
  * dependency on SWT_AWT and thus SunJava
  * testet only under linux

